reviewText:
I saw this movie about 10 years ago.

The only problem I had with receiving it was that the box was crushed a bit.

Thanks for sending it so quickly and the price was great!!

when seen this movie on cable had to have it i was concern it was a third party seller but i  was not disappointed for the price i was very pleased fast shipping and the quality of the movie was  very good
Saw this movie on television, best I had seen in decades.  My only problem when I went to purchase, it was on VHS.
After stumbling across this film surfing the internet,I watched with much interest. II then wondered why I had never even heard of the film. It was really good. I recommend it wholly.
